data.name: /knowledgegraph/entities/

description: Ambiverse Natural Language Understanding API extracts entities from unstructured text, enabling a more precise transformation of texts into actionable, measurable, and easily accessible knowledge. Entities are identified by types such as person, location, organization, or product, and linked to the Wikipedia-derived YAGO knowledge graph. You can query the knowledge graph to obtain further information about these entities, such as Wikipedia links, textual descriptions, images, and lists of relevant categories.
